[http://www.belkin.com/IWCatProductPage.process?Product_Id=377018 Product page] "YKM00D-1.6" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. [http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?p=635869 Post purporting a supported firmware image on the DD-WRT forums] The default SSID pattern may be '''Belkin_N1_Wireless_XXXXXX''' or '''Belkin_N1_XXXXXX''' (where '''XXXXXX''' is the last three octets of the wireless interface MAC [upper case hex characters]).
